JOHANNESBURG - The blue-eyed IT specialist arrived for the interview wearing a simple, white T-shirt, and jeans, and appeared to be an ordinary guy. What is it about the humble Hlompho Maseko that has brought him more than 50,900 followers and more than 5,000 friends on Facebook? *Watch part 1 of 2 here: He begins by sharing how he was astounded by the number of people engaging with his vlogs. "I've got a following of over 50,000 people and most of them are women. The reason is that woman are somehow looking for hope in good men out there and in life" Despite the overwhelming support and high-level engagement, he explicitly stated that he has no aspirations to become a socialite or celebrity. Maseko wants to continue speaking and uplifting ordinary people who experience life just as he does, he said. eNCA